text: Kim Song-hui () is the name of: *Kim Song-hui (speed skater) (born 1965), North Korean speed skater *Kim Song-hui (table tennis) (born 1968), North Korean table tennis player *Kim Song-hui (footballer) (born 1987), North Korean association footballer ==See also== *Kim Sung-hee (born 1989), South Korean singer and former member of the girl band Kara (South Korean band)
title: Kim Song-hui
